OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of
OL,7,Ffootballer Maddy Cusack has been
OL,8,Fadjourned for the second time this
OL,9,Fyear, nearly three years after she
OL,10,Fdied.
OL,12,FThe Sheffield United player was found
OL,13,Funresponsive at her home in Horsley,
OL,14,FDerbyshire, on 20 September, 2023.
OL,16,FChesterfield Coroner's Court heard
OL,17,Fthat the 27-year-old died after her
OL,18,Fcoach Jonathan Morgan made comments
OL,19,Fabout her weight and relationship.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
