PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FThe inquest was told the player's
OL,7,Ffamily sent a written complaint to
OL,8,FUnited within a week of her death,
OL,9,Foutlining issues they alleged stemmed
OL,10,Ffrom her time working under Mr Morgan.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, after eight days of
OL,13,Fevidence, Assistant Coroner Sophie
OL,14,FCartwright KC told Miss Cusack's
OL,15,Ffamily the inquest would be adjourned
OL,16,Funtil 7 December to obtain further
OL,17,Finformation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FThe inquest was due to hear its final
OL,7,Fevidence this week and the coroner had
OL,8,Fbeen expected to deliver her
OL,9,Fconclusion on 27 July.
OL,11,FThe inquest was meant to begin in
OL,12,FJanuary but was postponed just before
OL,13,FChristmas because of delays in the
OL,14,Fdisclosure of information to Miss
OL,15,FCusack's family.
OL,17,FMs Cartwright told the family: "I know
OL,18,Fhow long you have waited for this
OL,19,Finquest.
OL,26,@yD@`OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
