PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,F"I genuinely am sorry to the family
OL,7,Fand the properly interested persons.
OL,8,FThe hope we would finish today or
OL,9,Ftomorrow will not take place for
OL,10,Freasons you know."
OL,12,FShe added that her thoughts will be
OL,13,Fwith the Cusack family on the third
OL,14,Fanniversary of Miss Cusack's death and
OL,15,Fher birthday in the period before the
OL,16,Finquest resumes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]
