CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FMs Cartwright said the club will be
OL,7,Fasked to look into its Teams folders
OL,8,Fand Google Drive records for any
OL,9,Finformation related to Miss Cusack,
OL,10,Fand an audit of her health records on
OL,11,Fthe club's system in the months before
OL,12,Fshe died will be requested.
OL,14,FDr Subhashis Basu, the former club
OL,15,Fdoctor, and Francesca Carr, who was
OL,16,Fthe head physiotherapist for the
OL,17,Fwomen's team, will be recalled to give
OL,18,Ffurther evidence, the coroner said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
