PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FThe court also heard that Miss
OL,7,FCusack's mother, Deborah Cusack, may
OL,8,Fbe called again.
OL,10,FThe inquest has not yet heard from
OL,11,FVicki Anderson, United's head of HR,
OL,12,Fand David Matthews, the Football
OL,13,FAssociation's head of integrity.
OL,15,FThe coroner has already heard from
OL,16,FMiss Cusack's parents, her former
OL,17,Fteammates, Mr Morgan, and members of
OL,18,Fstaff from the club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
