PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783707575
OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FMrs Cusack said her daughter was
OL,7,F"absolutely devastated" about Mr
OL,8,FMorgan joining the club in February
OL,9,F2023 because of her experience working
OL,10,Fwith him years earlier at Leicester
OL,11,FCity, and worried that "history was
OL,12,Frepeating itself".
OL,14,FThe inquest previously heard that Mr
OL,15,FMorgan called Miss Cusack "bottom
OL,16,Fheavy", which he said was referencing
OL,17,Fher muscular legs, and said "here come
OL,18,Fthe girlfriends" when she was walking
OL,19,Fwith her partner and United teammate
OL,20,FGrace Riglar.
