OL,3,CInquest into death of footballer Maddy
OL,4,CCusack adjourned again
OL,6,FHe denied calling Miss Cusack a
OL,7,F"psycho" from the sidelines during a
OL,8,Fmatch before he was appointed manager
OL,9,Fat United.
OL,11,FMr Morgan told the inquest that he
OL,12,Fsupported the midfielder and was
OL,13,F"really happy" to keep her on his team.
